title: exec()
brief: Execute a program, interactively.
version: 0.07
----

<p>The <span class="tt">exec</span> function will reset the screen to allow you to run an interactive program without seeing any garbled display artifacts.</p>
<p>You might use it as follows:</p>
<pre>
exec( "top" );
</pre>
<p>When the program terminates the screen will be reset, and the current display restored.</p>